11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14void fill6bits(bits, msk)
15 int bits;
16 u_int *msk;
17{
18 if (bits == 0) {
19 msk[0] = 0;
20 msk[1] = 0;
21 msk[2] = 0;
22 msk[3] = 0;
23 return;
24 }
25
26 msk[0] = 0xffffffff;
27 msk[1] = 0xffffffff;
28 msk[2] = 0xffffffff;
29 msk[3] = 0xffffffff;
30
31 if (bits == 128)
32 return;
33 if (bits > 96) {
34 msk[3] = htonl(msk[3] << (128 - bits));
35 } else if (bits > 64) {
36 msk[3] = 0;
37 msk[2] = htonl(msk[2] << (96 - bits));
38 } else if (bits > 32) {
39 msk[3] = 0;
40 msk[2] = 0;
41 msk[1] = htonl(msk[1] << (64 - bits));
42 } else {
43 msk[3] = 0;
44 msk[2] = 0;
45 msk[1] = 0;
46 msk[0] = htonl(msk[0] << (32 - bits));
47 }
48}
